-- MOVES-Trevor Stokes joins Sovereign Capital as investment manager
-- By Lehar Maan in Bengaluru
-- Mon Dec 15, 2014 07:42AM EST
-- None



Dec 15 (Reuters) - UK-based private equity firm Sovereign Capital appointed Trevor Stokes as investment manager and Oliver Hedley-Whyte as investment executive.

Stokes most recently worked at financial advisory firm Global Leisure Partners in the role of vice president. Oliver joins Sovereign from August Equity where his role entailed execution of deals within the business services, healthcare and technology sectors.